data.description: Welcome to your next opportunity! This single-family home in the desirable Lake Dow North community is just waiting for the right family to turn it into a stunning home. This home is ideal for a first-time home buyer or investor. With 4 generously sized bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this property offers plenty of space for families of all sizes. The main bedroom boasts a walk-in closet and en-suite bathroom for ultimate comfort and privacy. Plus, there are three additional generously sized bedrooms that can accommodate a large family or provide space for a home office, workout room, or guest rooms. One of the standout features of this property is the large backyard, perfect for outdoor activities and gatherings with family and friends. The two-car garage and spacious driveway provide ample parking for multiple vehicles, while the handicap ramp offers easy wheelchair accessibility. Located in the Lake Dow North community, this property is surrounded by upscale homes and a thriving community. The area is known for its excellent schools, scenic lake views, and a strong sense of community. Plus, the nearby shopping and dining options offer convenience and easy access to all of life's necessities. Don't miss out on this incredible investment opportunity! With a little TLC and the right vision, this property has the potential to become a stunning family home that will attract for years to come.
